@startuml IntegrationRedmine
title TIMELAPSE - Integração Redmine (RF003, RF004)
participant Timelapse
participant RedmineAdapter
participant RedmineAPI

Timelapse -> RedmineAdapter: Request Sync (lastCheckpoint)
RedmineAdapter -> RedmineAPI: GET /issues.json?updated_on=>checkpoint
RedmineAPI -> RedmineAdapter: JSON (issues)

RedmineAdapter -> RedmineAdapter: Map RedmineIssue -> TimelapseTask
RedmineAdapter -> RedmineAdapter: Map status, tracker, priority
RedmineAdapter -> Timelapse: Return Normalized Data

note over RedmineAdapter
  Conversão de metadados
  Redmine -> Padrão interno
  (RF005)
end note
@enduml
